'''深盤披薩'''（{{lang-en|Deep-dish pizza}}），又叫「厚底薄-{}-餅」、「番茄批」<ref>{{cite web|title=【千奇百趣】芝加哥發明3.5厘米厚薄餅 填滿芝士茄醬食兩塊就飽|url=http://hk.news.yahoo.com/千奇百趣-芝加哥發明3-5厘米厚薄餅-填滿芝士茄醬食兩塊就飽-045514972.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181121055304/http://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E3%80%90%E5%8D%83%E5%A5%87%E7%99%BE%E8%B6%A3%E3%80%91%E8%8A%9D%E5%8A%A0%E5%93%A5%E7%99%BC%E6%98%8E3-5%E5%8E%98%E7%B1%B3%E5%8E%9A%E8%96%84%E9%A4%85-%E5%A1%AB%E6%BB%BF%E8%8A%9D%E5%A3%AB%E8%8C%84-050814834.html|archivedate=2018-11-21|access-date=2022-01-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是一種發源於[[美國|美國]][[芝加哥|芝加哥]]的特色[[披薩|披薩]]<ref>Ali, Tanveer; Ludwig, Howard (January 13, 2015). [http://www.dnainfo.com/chicago/20150113/chicago/guide-chicago-pizza-from-deep-dish-tavern-style-beyond "A Guide to Chicago Pizza: From Deep-Dish to Tavern-Style and Beyond"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160101171634/http://www.dnainfo.com/chicago/20150113/chicago/guide-chicago-pizza-from-deep-dish-tavern-style-beyond |date=2016-01-01 }}, DNAinfo. Retrieved January 2, 2016.</ref>，與一般的披薩相比，它的厚度特別的厚，達5公分。目前尚沒有足夠的文獻來確定誰發明了芝加哥風格的深盤披薩<ref>[http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2009-02-18/news/0902180055_1_chicago-pizza-ric-riccardo-pizzeria-uno"Who Invented Deep Dish?"] {{Wayback|url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2009-02-18/news/0902180055_1_chicago-pizza-ric-riccardo-pizzeria-uno |date=20140318014935 }}, ''Chicago Tribune'', February 18, 2009. Retrieved January 2, 2016.</ref>。

深盤披薩是用鐵鍋或圓形鋼鍋烤製的，外型顯得更像[[西式餡餅|派]]或[[餡餅|餡餅]]，中間填滿餡料與大量起司。

